     CODES ARE NOW AVAILABLE FOR SPECIFYING FREQUENCY SLOPED COMPENSATION.
 5.  STRIPLINE AND MICROSTRIP OPTIONS FOR THE CIRCULAR STUB (CST).
 6.  THREE NEW AERTECH DEVICES ADDED TO TRANSISTOR DATABANK,
